data.chText: 浪费好好的食物是有罪的！
data.enText: It's sinful to waste good food!

tr: far more than usual or expected
wicked because it is believed to be a sin
example: he said it was sinful to wear lipstick

value.def: If you describe someone or something as sinful, you mean that they are wicked or immoral.

example.ex: 'I am a sinful man,' he said.
He reminded us that smoking was sinful.
example.tran: 他提醒我们吸烟是不道德的。
